  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="How Much Does House Cleaning Cost in Alabama? (2025 Pricing Guide)"
    description="Real house cleaning prices in Alabama for 2025. What to expect for deep cleaning, recurring service, move-out cleaning in Huntsville, Birmingham, Nashville. Transparent pricing guide."
